---
// Privacy Policy page
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy | Fresh Wax</title>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="legal-container">
    <div class="legal-card">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <a href="/" class="logo-link">
          <div class="logo-wrapper">
            <img src="/logo.webp" alt="Fresh Wax" class="logo-img">
          </div>
        </a>
        <h1><span class="fresh">Fresh</span> <span class="wax">Wax</span></h1>
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 2024</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <section>
          <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
          <p>When you use Fresh Wax, we collect:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Email address, display name, and password</li>
            <li><strong>Profile information:</strong> Artist name, bio, and links (if applicable)</li>
            <li><strong>Purchase history:</strong> Records of your transactions</li>
            <li><strong>Content:</strong> DJ mixes, comments, and ratings you submit</li>
            <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> How you interact with the platform</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
          <p>We use your information to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and maintain the Fresh Wax platform</li>
            <li>Process purchases and deliver digital content</li>
            <li>Enable community features (comments, ratings, mixes)</li>
            <li>Communicate with you about your account and orders</li>
            <li>Improve our services</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>3. Information Sharing</h3>
          <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Payment processors:</strong> To complete transactions</li>
            <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Who help us operate the platform</li>
            <li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> When required by law</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Your public profile, uploaded mixes, comments, and ratings are visible to other users.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>4. Data Storage</h3>
          <p>Your data is stored securely using industry-standard practices. We use Firebase and Cloudflare services to host and protect your information.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your account and data</li>
            <li>Download your uploaded content</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us through the platform.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>6. Cookies</h3>
          <p>We use essential cookies for authentication and session management. We may use analytics cookies to understand how the platform is used.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>7. Third-Party Links</h3>
          <p>Our platform may contain links to external sites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of other websites.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>8. Children's Privacy</h3>
          <p>Fresh Wax is not intended for users under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>9. Changes to This Policy</h3>
          <p>We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes through the platform or by email.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>10. Contact</h3>
          <p>For privacy-related questions, please contact us through the platform.</p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-footer">
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Back to Register</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    .legal-container {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: var(--bg-primary, #0a0a0a);
    }

    .legal-card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 700px;
      background: var(--bg-secondary, #141414);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color, #262626);
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .legal-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color, #262626);
    }

    .logo-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .logo-wrapper {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }

    .logo-img {
      max-width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .legal-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .legal-header h1 .fresh {
      color: #fff;
    }

    .legal-header h1 .wax {
      color: #ef4444;
    }

    .legal-header h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--text-primary, #fff);
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }

    .last-updated {
      color: var(--text-muted, #666);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .legal-content {
      color: var(--text-secondary, #a3a3a3);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .legal-content section {
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }

    .legal-content h3 {
      color: var(--text-primary, #fff);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .legal-content p {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .legal-content ul {
      margin: 0.75rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .legal-content li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .legal-content strong {
      color: var(--text-primary, #fff);
    }

    .legal-footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color, #262626);
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #ef4444;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #dc2626;
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
